<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Peluquería Canina Snoopy - Contacto</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
   <!-- BOOTSTRAP CSS only-->
   <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
   <!-- CSS PROPIO -->

   <!-- font awesome-->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
   <style>
     .navbar {
       margin: 0;
       border-radius: 0;
     }
     body {
       text-justify: auto;
       font-family: 'Lucida Sans';
       background-image: url(/public/images/patron_patitas\ 70x70.png);
       background-repeat: repeat; 
     }
  
    footer {
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
      padding: 25px;
    }

    .carousel-inner > .item > img {
      min-width: 100%;
      width: 100%;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .carousel-caption {
        display: none;
      }
    }

    .contact-form-container {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); /* White with 80% opacity */
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Navigation bar -->
  <%- include('./partials/navigation.ejs') %>
  <!-- Navigation bar -->

  <div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="contact-form-container">
      <h2>Contacto</h2>
      <p>Para cualquier consulta, rellene el siguiente formulario y nos pondremos en contacto con usted lo antes posible.</p>

      <form>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="name" class="form-label">Nombre:</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" placeholder="Ingrese su nombre" required>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="email" class="form-label">Correo electrónico:</label>
          <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="Ingrese su correo electrónico" required>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="message" class="form-label">Mensaje:</label>
          <textarea class="form-control" id="message" rows="5" placeholder="Escriba su mensaje" required></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Enviar</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>
  <!-- Fin Footer -->

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="../public/js/general-user.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
